{
  "texts": [
    "The algorithm then replaces the top 𝑛 most significant subtrees in 𝑄 𝑎 with subtrees from 𝑄 𝑏 of the same syntactic category in lines 9-11.",
    "This process aims to generate new queries that can effectively evaluate the model's ability to identify and handle malicious queries.In this method, we apply two strategies to reduce the generation of nonsensical queries.",
    "First, during the replacement process, our approach is to maintain the structural integrity of the syntactic tree.",
    "This is achieved by substituting syntactic subtrees with alternatives of the same syntactic category.",
    "This method ensures that the overall structure of the sentence remains intact, thereby preserving grammatical correctness."
  ]
